Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
