Dialogue: 0,2:52:37.20,2:52:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 这反应
Dialogue: 0,2:52:40.21,2:52:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:52:45.48,2:52:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:52:50.22,2:52:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我来用干净 谢谢
